Programming Language

Python 3.x
Primary language used for ETL orchestration, reconciliation logic, validation engine, aggregation modeling, and monitoring framework.

Key Libraries:
	•	pandas – data transformation and financial modeling
	•	sqlalchemy – secure database interaction layer
	•	snowflake-connector-python – Snowflake connectivity
	•	python-dotenv – environment configuration management
	•	logging – structured execution logging
	•	pytest – unit testing framework

